<div class="greeting">
  Hi {{firstName}},
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>This is a friendly reminder that your rent payment is due soon.</p>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3>Payment Details</h3>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Amount Due:</span>
    <span class="info-value"><strong>KES {{amount}}</strong></span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Due Date:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{dueDate}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Property:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{propertyAddress}}</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>To avoid late fees, please make your payment before the due date.</p>
</div>

<a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="button">Pay Now</a>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>Payment Methods:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>M-Pesa: Pay via STK Push in the portal</li>
    <li>Bank Transfer: Use your unique reference number</li>
    <li>Cash: Visit our office during business hours</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>If you've already made this payment, please disregard this reminder.</p>
  <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@nyumbasync.co.ke">support@nyumbasync.co.ke</a> or call 0700NYUMBA.</p>
</div>
